Och-Ziff Capital Management - Wikipedia






















 






Och-Ziff Capital Management

From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia
  (Redirected from Och-Ziff Capital Management Group LLC)

					Jump to:					navigation, 					search


Och-Ziff Capital Management Group LLC (DBA: OZ Management)





Type

Public company


Traded as
NYSE: OZM


Industry
Hedge funds


Founded
1994; 23 years ago (1994)


Founder
Daniel Och


