Home / Companies / Och-Ziff Capital Management Group LLC


Och-Ziff Capital Management Group LLC

9 West 57th Street 39th Floor 
New York NY 10019 United States
Phone: +1 212-___-____
Fax: +1 212-___-____
http://www.ozcap.com





25
Managers




35
IT employees




$7.8MEST.
IT Budget




Och-Ziff is a hedge fund and alternative assent management firm. They have a diversified portfolio of non-traditional investments and operate out of offices in New York, London, Hong Kong, Bangalore, Tokyo and Beijing.
Och-Ziff's IT department is run by the Chief Information Officer, who is directly supported by the Chief Technology Officer. The CIO is responsible for information security and, along with project managers, oversees the creation and integration of new trading software… MoreOch-Ziff's IT department is run by the Chief Information Officer, who is directly supported by the Chief Technology Officer. The CIO is responsible for information security and, along with project managers, oversees the creation and integration of new trading software and trading desk systems.

The CTO is responsible for the hardware used by the company, including networking equipment, servers, and telecommunication systems. He is also responsible for the website.

Financial applications have their own development team which operates largely under the supervision of the finance department.

The company uses external and contract IT employees on a project-by-project basis.





